
Component_System_Library.fig
AECS — AvizSazeh Engineering UX System

This is a structured Figma-style specification file (not binary Figma format).

========================
1. CORE COMPONENTS
========================

SystemHero:
- type: hero
- props: title, subtitle, CTA, backgroundType
- behavior: fade-in + system reveal

SystemModuleCard:
- type: card
- props: title, logic, diagramPreview, systemType
- behavior: hover expand engineering logic

ProjectCaseCard:
- type: case-study
- props: problem, solution, executionImage, engineeringSteps
- behavior: progressive reveal on scroll

EngineeringFlow:
- type: diagram
- props: steps [Design, Engineering, Manufacturing, Execution]
- behavior: sequential activation

RFQEngine:
- type: form-system
- props: projectType, area, systemType, files, constraints
- behavior: step-based system input

TrustBar:
- type: metrics
- props: projectsCount, regions, systemsCount
- behavior: static with subtle highlight

========================
2. LAYOUT COMPONENTS
========================

GridSystem:
- columns: 12 desktop / 8 tablet / 4 mobile
- spacing: 8px base system

SectionBlock:
- full-width system container
- behavior: vertical stack

SplitBlock:
- 50/50 layout
- used for text + diagram

CardGrid:
- 3-column system layout

StackFlow:
- vertical step system (RFQ / engineering flow)

========================
3. DESIGN RULES
========================

- no decorative UI
- all components must map to engineering logic
- spacing must follow 8px grid
- motion = structural only

========================
END OF FILE
